<chapter xml:id="chap-examples" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Examples with source</title>

  <p>This chapter presents a series of <prefigure/> diagrams along
  with their source.  These examples may provide a starting point for
  authors to explore in the
  <url href="https://davidaustinm.github.io/prefigure">
    <prefigure/> Playground.
  </url>
  </p>

